tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE hospital_reports (
  report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  hospital_name VARCHAR(50),
  patient_outcomes VARCHAR(50),
  resource_utilization VARCHAR(50)
)
CREATE TABLE Hospital_Performance (    hospital_id INT PRIMARY KEY,    performance_rating FLOAT,    report_date DATE );
CREATE TABLE Patient_Outcomes (    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,    outcome_type VARCHAR(50),    outcome_description TEXT,    discharge_date DATE );
CREATE TABLE Resource_Utilization (    resource_id INT PRIMARY KEY,    resource_name VARCHAR(50),    resource_type VARCHAR(50),    usage_date DATE );
CREATE TABLE Hospital_Staff (    staff_id INT PRIMARY KEY,    staff_name VARCHAR(50),    staff_role VARCHAR(50) );
